<p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: 28.4444px; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;">　　<strong><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 28.4444px; orphans: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">而妹妹陈难却选择给</span></strong></p>
<p style="white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: #3e3e3e; line-height: 28.4444px; background-color: #ffffff; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;">　　<span style="letter-spacing: 1px; color: #7b0c00;"><strong><span style="color: #7b0c00; letter-spacing: 1px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28.4444px; orphans: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">日军的妻子</span></strong></span><strong><span style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 28.4444px; orphans: 2; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">写了一封信！</span></strong></p>
